 .panel-title a.hover .fa-fusion-box { background-color: var(--awb-color4)!important;border-color: var(--awb-color4)!important;}<\/style><div class=\"fusion-faq-shortcode\" style=\"\"><div class=\"fusion-faqs-wrapper\"><div class=\"accordian fusion-accordian\"><div class=\"panel-group \" id=\"accordian-1\"><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default fusion-faq-post fusion-faq-post-1518 summer-makhtab summer-program \"><span class=\"entry-title rich-snippet-hidden\">What are the Makhtab program rules?<\/span><span class=\"vcard rich-snippet-hidden\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"https:\/\/mhma.us\/author\/asif-ruhigmail-com\/\" title=\"Posts by Asif Mohammed\" rel=\"author\">Asif Mohammed<\/a><\/span><\/span><span class=\"updated rich-snippet-hidden\">2026-03-02T15:51:07-08:00<\/span><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"faq_1-1518\" class=\"panel-title toggle\"><a data-toggle=\"collapse\" class=\"collapsed\" data-parent=\"#accordian-1\" data-target=\"#collapse-1-1518\" href=\"#collapse-1-1518\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><div class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper-main\"><div class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper-sub\"><i class=\"fa-fusion-box active-icon awb-icon-minus\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><i class=\"fa-fusion-box inactive-icon awb-icon-plus\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-toggle-heading\">What are the Makhtab program rules?<\/div><\/a><\/h4><\/div><div id=\"collapse-1-1518\" aria-labelledby=\"faq_1-1518\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content post-content\"><ol>\n<li>Students must arrive on time and be picked up on time every day.<\/li>\n<li>Students must come to class wearing clean clothes.<\/li>\n<li>Students must come to class wearing modest attire (loose clothing).\u00a0 Full hijab must be Observed by the girls and boys are encouraged to wear Kufi (headgear). Students are not allowed to sit in class wearing shorts, tight or indecent clothing.<\/li>\n<li>Students must be respectful to the teachers, peers, and the facility at all times. Any form of disrespect will NOT be tolerated at all.<\/li>\n<li>Students are not allowed to leave the facility premises without permission from the teacher or staff member on duty.<\/li>\n<li>Students are not allowed to use any electronic devices in the class.<\/li>\n<li>Students are not allowed to bring any item to class that can be a distraction to themselves or other students of the class.<\/li>\n<li>Students are not allowed to bring food or drinks to the class.<\/li>\n<li>Students are not allowed to bring any dangerous item to class, knife etc.<\/li>\n<li>Students must be punctual with their attendance in our school.<\/li>\n<li>Students must complete their homework on time.<\/li>\n<li>Parents must sign the child\u2019s progress report every week. If it is not signed, the teacher will send a reminder to the parents. If the problem continues then it could impact your child\u2019s participation in our program.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><b>Violations:<\/b><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>The first violation will result in a talk with the student.<\/li>\n<li>The second violation will result in a meeting with the parents.<\/li>\n<li>Third violation will result in suspension or possible expulsion. The consequences are at the discretion of the teachers and staff.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default fusion-faq-post fusion-faq-post-1520 summer-makhtab summer-program \"><span class=\"entry-title rich-snippet-hidden\">What are the guidelines for the parents?<\/span><span class=\"vcard rich-snippet-hidden\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"https:\/\/mhma.us\/author\/asif-ruhigmail-com\/\" title=\"Posts by Asif Mohammed\" rel=\"author\">Asif Mohammed<\/a><\/span><\/span><span class=\"updated rich-snippet-hidden\">2024-06-01T19:41:00-07:00<\/span><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"faq_1-1520\" class=\"panel-title toggle\"><a data-toggle=\"collapse\" class=\"collapsed\" data-parent=\"#accordian-1\" data-target=\"#collapse-1-1520\" href=\"#collapse-1-1520\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><div class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper-main\"><div class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper-sub\"><i class=\"fa-fusion-box active-icon awb-icon-minus\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><i class=\"fa-fusion-box inactive-icon awb-icon-plus\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-toggle-heading\">What are the guidelines for the parents?<\/div><\/a><\/h4><\/div><div id=\"collapse-1-1520\" aria-labelledby=\"faq_1-1520\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content post-content\"><ul>\n<li>Parents should show importance to their child\u2019s Islamic education, if we do not show importance how can we expect our children to show importance.<\/li>\n<li>Like any other type of education, a necessary component of your child\u2019s success starts from your own home.\u00a0 The more effort you make in your child\u2019s studies the more he will succeed.<\/li>\n<li>Parents should be informed of what their child is learning in school.<\/li>\n<li>Parents should ensure their child arrives to class on time and leaves class on time. Every minute matters!<\/li>\n<li>They should check their WhatsApp daily for any updates by teachers &amp; admins. This will be the main way of communication between staff and parents.<\/li>\n<li>Parents are NOT allowed to have conversations with one another near the class where it becomes a distraction to the class.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default fusion-faq-post fusion-faq-post-1522 summer-makhtab summer-program \"><span class=\"entry-title rich-snippet-hidden\">What is the Curriculum of the Maktab program?<\/span><span class=\"vcard rich-snippet-hidden\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"https:\/\/mhma.us\/author\/asif-ruhigmail-com\/\" title=\"Posts by Asif Mohammed\" rel=\"author\">Asif Mohammed<\/a><\/span><\/span><span class=\"updated rich-snippet-hidden\">2026-03-02T15:56:36-08:00<\/span><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"faq_1-1522\" class=\"panel-title toggle\"><a data-toggle=\"collapse\" class=\"collapsed\" data-parent=\"#accordian-1\" data-target=\"#collapse-1-1522\" href=\"#collapse-1-1522\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><div class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper-main\"><div class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper-sub\"><i class=\"fa-fusion-box active-icon awb-icon-minus\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><i class=\"fa-fusion-box inactive-icon awb-icon-plus\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-toggle-heading\">What is the Curriculum of the Maktab program?<\/div><\/a><\/h4><\/div><div id=\"collapse-1-1522\" aria-labelledby=\"faq_1-1522\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content post-content\"><ol>\n<li><b>Quran<\/b> \u2013 teaching Qaidah with correct pronunciation, reading Quran, and memorizing of surahs.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Tajweed<\/strong> \u2013 Teaching tajweed rules with its application.<\/li>\n<li><b>Islamic studies<\/b> \u2013 Consisting of basic Aqeedah, Seerah, fiqh, quranic stories, hadiths and other general Islamic Studies.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li><b>Fiqh<\/b>: Learning the laws regarding wudhu, ghusl, salaah, and other daily ibadaat<\/li>\n<li><b>Surahs &amp; Du\u2019aas<\/b>: Memorizing short surahs and du\u2019aas with their translation and understanding.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default fusion-faq-post fusion-faq-post-1524 summer-makhtab summer-program \"><span class=\"entry-title rich-snippet-hidden\">Who are the teachers of the Makhtab program?<\/span><span class=\"vcard rich-snippet-hidden\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"https:\/\/mhma.us\/author\/asif-ruhigmail-com\/\" title=\"Posts by Asif Mohammed\" rel=\"author\">Asif Mohammed<\/a><\/span><\/span><span class=\"updated rich-snip